<p>Categories are automatically filled from the PANOSE metadata in the font files. These filter all font files by </p>

<list>
<item><p>Family Kind</p></item>
<item><p>Spacing</p></item>
<item><p>Slant</p></item>
<item><p>Weight</p></item>
<item><p>Width</p></item>
<item><p>Filetype</p></item>
<item><p>License</p></item>
<item><p>Vendor</p></item>
</list>

<p>Additionally, this view distinguishes by fonts installed system-wide and versus installed by the current user. <!--needs more info? i did not find out how this is done and what is the real impact - (using a one-user system)}--></p>

